 39.8241%; justify-content: center;\"><div data-ce-tag=\"toggle\"><input data-ce-tag=\"toggleradio\" id=\"pbs-toggle-89aser\" type=\"checkbox\">  <label data-ce-tag=\"toggletab\" for=\"pbs-toggle-89aser\">  Text Search  </label>  <div class=\"pbs-row\" style><div class=\"pbs-col\">\n\nThe Text Search filter can be found in the form of a search field on a bar at the top of both the Record List and the Map Interface. Searching in the text box will narrow down the incidents to ones that include the search term in a field marked as filterable/searchable in the database designer. Typing multiple words will perform a search for incidents that have both of the words in one or more fields.\n\n</div></div></div>\n<div data-ce-tag=\"toggle\"><input data-ce-tag=\"toggleradio\" id=\"pbs-toggle-nd36jq\" type=\"checkbox\">  <label data-ce-tag=\"toggletab\" for=\"pbs-toggle-nd36jq\">  Date Filter  </label>  <div class=\"pbs-row\" style><div class=\"pbs-col\">\n\nThe Date Filter can usually be found in between the Text Search Filter and the Option Filter, and narrows down incident data according to a date interval set by the user. Clicking on the Date Filter launches a clickable interface to choose minimum and maximum dates for display and analysis. The default range of the Date Filter is the previous ninety days.\n\n</div></div></div>\n<div data-ce-tag=\"toggle\"><input data-ce-tag=\"toggleradio\" id=\"pbs-toggle-ptvs10\" type=\"checkbox\">  <label data-ce-tag=\"toggletab\" for=\"pbs-toggle-ptvs10\">  Option Filter  </label>  <div class=\"pbs-row\" style><div class=\"pbs-col\">\n\nOption filters are shown in the form of enumeration fields (such as select lists and checkboxes), and are included as attribute filter dropdown buttons. Examples of option filters include Reporting Agency (concerned in the incident), Main Cause (of the incident), and Severity (of the incident). Selecting an option applies that filter to the data, and multiple options may be selected for any filter. Active filters are highlighted in light blue in the interface.\n\n</div></div></div>\n<div data-ce-tag=\"toggle\"><input data-ce-tag=\"toggleradio\" id=\"pbs-toggle-i93vk7\" type=\"checkbox\">  <label data-ce-tag=\"toggletab\" for=\"pbs-toggle-i93vk7\">  Numeric Filter  </label>  <div class=\"pbs-row\" style><div class=\"pbs-col\">\n\nFields containing numbers may be filtered using a minimum/maximum range in the numeric filter.\n\n</div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pbs-col\" style=\"flex-basis: 60.1747%; justify-content: center;\"></div></div>\n<h3>  <span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Related Articles</span>  </h3>  <ul>  <li>  <a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/view-interfaces\">View Interfaces</a>  </li>  <li>  <a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/map\">Map Interface</a>  </li>  <li>  <a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/attribute-filters\">Attribute Filters</a>  </li>  </ul>', 'Record List', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-27 12:20:49', '2017-09-27 12:20:49', '', 70, 'http://roadsafety.ph/2017/09/27/70-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
