(409, 1, '2017-09-29 13:19:29', '2017-09-29 13:19:29', '[:en]\r\nDRIVER is designed to collect and analyze data about incidents that occur at a particular place, such as traffic accidents or crimes. The application provides data entry tools, graph and map interfaces, custom report and filter tools, multiple concurrent user editing, and data exports.\r\n\r\nSigning In\r\n\r\nView Interfaces\r\n\r\nFilters\r\n\r\nView Interfaces (Map vs Record List)\r\n\r\nFilters\r\n\r\nLayers\r\n\r\nExporting Data\r\n\r\n[:Ph]\r\nAng DRIVER ay ginawa para mangolekta at mapag-aralan ang mga insidente na nangyayari sa iba\'t ibang lugar, tulad ng mga aksidenteng dulot ng trapiko o mga krimen. The application provides data entry tools, graph and map interfaces, custom report and filter tools, multiple concurrent user editing, and data exports.\r\n\r\nSigning In\r\n\r\nView Interfaces\r\n\r\nFilters\r\n\r\nView Interfaces (Map vs Record List)\r\n\r\nFilters\r\n\r\nLayers\r\n\r\nExporting Data\r\n\r\n[:]', '[:en]About DRIVER[:Ph]Tungkol sa DRIVER[:tl]Getting Started[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '172-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-29 13:19:29', '2017-09-29 13:19:29', '', 172, 'http://roadsafety.ph/172-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
