(446, 1, '2017-09-29 14:42:58', '2017-09-29 14:42:58', '[:en]Economic loss and societal harm costs are calculated based on an Ashlar configuration. Administrators choose an option-type field associated with the primary record type, such as “Severity”, and associate a cost with each of its values.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn the DRIVER interface, this cost is displayed both in the dashboard and map views. The cost totals respect the geographic, temporal, and attribute filters applied in the map. This makes it possible for a user to associate an estimated cost for a search like <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">crashes involving pedestrians in a certain neighborhood in 2016.</span>[:Ph]\r\nEconomic loss and societal harm costs are calculated based on an Ashlar configuration. Administrators choose an option-type field associated with the primary record type, such as “Severity”, and associate a cost with each of its values.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\">SCREENSHOT HERE</span>\r\n\r\nIn the DRIVER interface, this cost is displayed both in the dashboard and map views. The cost totals respect the geographic, temporal, and attribute filters applied in the map. This makes it possible for a user to associate an estimated cost for a search like <span style=\"font-style:italic;\">crashes involving pedestrians in a certain neighborhood in 2016.</span>\r\n\r\n[:]', '[:en]Cost to Society[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '281-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-09-29 14:42:58', '2017-09-29 14:42:58', '', 281, 'http://roadsafety.ph/281-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(448, 1, '2017-10-02 03:09:16', '2017-10-02 03:09:16', '[:en]<h3><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Street View</span></h3>\r\nThe Street View option shows the user a simple roadmap view of the Philippines, which is the default map view on the DRIVER Dashboard.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-336 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screenshot_Zoom_Map.png\" width=\"1365\" height=\"588\" />\r\n<h3>Satelite View</h3>\r\nThe Satellite View option shows a pictured and more detailed view of the map, with data from OpenStreetMap.com. Users can switch between both the Satellite View and Street View by selecting the “Layers” option on the upper right corner of the map.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-338 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screenshot_Zoom_Satellite.png\" width=\"1365\" height=\"535\" />\r\n<h3>Related Notes</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Layers</li>\r\n 	<li>Geographic Boundaries</li>\r\n</ul>[:Ph]<h3>  <span style=\"font-weight:normal;\">Street View</span>  </h3>\r\n\r\nThe Street View option shows the user a simple roadmap view of the Philippines, which is the default map view on the DRIVER Dashboard.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-336 size-full\" height=\"588\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screenshot_Zoom_Map.png\" width=\"1365\">\r\n\r\n<h3>  Satelite View  </h3>\r\n\r\nThe Satellite View option shows a pictured and more detailed view of the map, with data from OpenStreetMap.com. Users can switch between both the Satellite View and Street View by selecting the “Layers” option on the upper right corner of the map.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-338 size-full\" height=\"535\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screenshot_Zoom_Satellite.png\" width=\"1365\">\r\n\r\n<h3>  Related Notes  </h3>  <ul>  <li>  Layers  </li>  <li>  Geographic Boundaries  </li>  </ul>[:]', '[:en]Native Layers[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '',