(690, 1, '2017-10-02 15:24:01', '2017-10-02 15:24:01', '[:en]<h3>How to Access the Record List</h3>\r\nTo access the record list, click on the “Dashboard” button on the topmost right corner of the website. A dropdown menu will appear, after which you may click the “Record List” button at the bottom of the list.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-672 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/02_Record-List_01-Click-Dashboard-1.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"443\" />\r\n<h3>Related Articles</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/view-interfaces\" xlink=\"href\">View Interfaces</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/attribute-filters/\" xlink=\"href\">Attribute Filters</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/map\" xlink=\"href\">Map Interface</a></li>\r\n</ul>[:]', '[:en]How to Access the Record List[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-access-the-record-list', '', '', '2017-10-02 15:24:01', '2017-10-02 15:24:01', '', 0, 'http://roadsafety.ph/?p=690', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(691, 1, '2017-10-02 15:24:01', '2017-10-02 15:24:01', '[:en]<h3>How to Access the Record List</h3>\r\nTo access the record list, click on the “Dashboard” button on the topmost right corner of the website. A dropdown menu will appear, after which you may click the “Record List” button at the bottom of the list.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-672 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/02_Record-List_01-Click-Dashboard-1.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"443\" />\r\n<h3>Related Articles</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/view-interfaces\" xlink=\"href\">View Interfaces</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/attribute-filters/\" xlink=\"href\">Attribute Filters</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/map\" xlink=\"href\">Map Interface</a></li>\r\n</ul>[:]', '[:en]How to Access the Record List[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '690-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-02 15:24:01', '2017-10-02 15:24:01', '', 690, 'http://roadsafety.ph/690-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(692, 1, '2017-10-02 15:25:40', '2017-10-02 15:25:40', '[:en]<h3><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/viewing-incident-data\" xlink=\"href\">Viewing Incident Data</a></h3>\r\nOn the right-most side of each entry in the list of incidents, you will find a button that says “View”.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-673 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/02_Record-List_02-Filtering_View-Incident.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"443\" />\r\n\r\nClicking on this will prompt the Incident Details window to appear, which shows more details of the incident data.\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/filtering-and-searching\" xlink=\"href\">Filtering &amp; Searching</a></h3>\r\nThe record list has a toolbar at the top of the page that allows the user access to the <a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/attribute-filters\" xlink=\"href\">Attribute Filters</a>, which is the primary type of filter used in the Record List.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-675 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Filters_Attribute-Filters-Copy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"103\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOn the Record List, the Attribute Filters allow users to narrow down incidents according to Name/Keyword, Date Range, Reporting Agency, Main Cause, and Severity.\r\n\r\nUsers may input any combination of these filters in order to further narrow down their search. Users may also opt to only input or apply one filter, or none at all.\r\n<h3>Related Articles</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/view-interfaces\" xlink=\"href\">View Interfaces</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/attribute-filters/\" xlink=\"href\">Attribute Filters</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/map\" xlink=\"href\">Map Interface</a></li>\r\n</ul>[:]', '[:en]Record List Tools[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'record-list-tools', '', '', '2017-10-03 08:29:22', '2017-10-03 08:29:22', '', 0, 'http://roadsafety.ph/?p=692', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(693, 1, '2017-10-02 15:25:40', '2017-10-02 15:25:40', '[:en]<h3>Viewing Incident Data</h3>\r\nOn the right-most side of each entry in the list of incidents, you will find a button that says “View”.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-673 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/02_Record-List_02-Filtering_View-Incident.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"443\" />\r\n\r\nClicking on this will prompt the Incident Details window to appear, which shows more details of the incident data.\r\n<h3>Filtering &amp; Searching<strong>\r\n</strong>The record list has a toolbar at the top of the page that allows the user access to the <a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/attribute-filters\" xlink=\"href\">Attribute Filters</a>, which is the primary type of filter used in the Record List.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-675 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Filters_Attribute-Filters-Copy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"103\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOn the Record List, the Attribute Filters allow users to narrow down incidents according to Name/Keyword, Date Range, Reporting Agency, Main Cause, and Severity.\r\n\r\nUsers may input any combination of these filters in order to further narrow down their search. Users may also opt to only input or apply one filter, or none at all.\r\n<h3>Related Articles</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/view-interfaces\" xlink=\"href\">View Interfaces</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/attribute-filters/\" xlink=\"href\">Attribute Filters</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://roadsafety.ph/map\" xlink=\"href\">Map Interface</a></li>\r\n</ul>[:]', '[:en]Record List Tools[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '692-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-02 15:25:40', '2017-10-02 15:25:40', '', 692, 'http://roadsafety.ph/692-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
