(818, 1, '2017-10-03 09:54:35', '2017-10-03 09:54:35', '[:en]Users can view Incident Reports and Locations through a variety of ways.\r\n<h3>Viewing from the Record List</h3>\r\nA full list of all incident reports may be accessed through the Record List. To view through the record list, click on the \"Dashboard\" button located on the top left corner of the dashboard:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-364 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/02_Record-List_01-Click-Dashboard.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"443\" />\r\n\r\nDoing this will lead you to a tabular view of all recorded incidents on DRIVER.\r\n\r\nOn the right-most side of each entry in the list of incidents, you will find a button that says “View”. Clicking on this will prompt the Incident Details popup to appear, which shows users more details of the incident data.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-809 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/02_Record-List_02-Filtering_View-Incident.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"443\" />\r\n<h3>Viewing from the Map</h3>\r\nTo view incidents from the map, first access the map page from the dashboard by clicking the \"Dashboard\" dropdown on the top left corner of the page, and clicking on \"Map.\"\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-811 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/01_Map_01-Click-Dashboard.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"443\" />\r\n\r\nFrom here, users may zoom in on the map and select any of the blue dots to view a specific incident:\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-358 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/01_Map_02-Zoom-In.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"444\" />\r\n<h3>Viewing Number of Incidents</h3>\r\nUsers can view the total number of incidents on the Incident widget on the dashboard:\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-797 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/01_DASHBOARD_After_Filter.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"639\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-817 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Screenshot_1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"352\" height=\"168\" />[:]', '[:en]Incident Reports & Locations[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '807-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-03 09:54:35', '2017-10-03 09:54:35', '', 807, 'http://roadsafety.ph/807-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
