(898, 1, '2017-10-04 01:08:55', '2017-10-04 01:08:55', '[:en]Interventions made regarding the incidents may also be recorded in DRIVER. Analyst users have the ability to add intervention records within the database.\r\n<h3>Accessing the Intervention Input Form</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-892 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ANALYST_Add_Intervention.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"87\" />\r\n\r\nTo add an Intervention, click on the \"Interventions\" tab at the bottom of the Map interface. A popup will appear that will prompt you to click on either \"Export Interventions\" or \"Add Intervention\".\" Click on the latter. This will prompt a new window to appear called \"Intervention Input Form\"\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-896 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ANALYST_Intervention_Input_Form_1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1366\" height=\"1203\" />\r\n\r\nFrom here, Analyst users may select the type of intervention made through a dropdown list available in the \"Intervention Detail\" category.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-897 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ANALYST_Intervention_Options.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"590\" />[:]', '[:en]Adding Interventions[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '891-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 01:08:55', '2017-10-04 01:08:55', '', 891, 'http://roadsafety.ph/891-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(899, 1, '2017-10-04 01:09:36', '2017-10-04 01:09:36', '[:en]Interventions made regarding the incidents may also be recorded in DRIVER. Analyst users have the ability to add intervention records within the database.\r\n<h3>Accessing the Intervention Input Form</h3>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-892 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ANALYST_Add_Intervention.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"87\" />\r\n\r\nTo add an Intervention, click on the \"Interventions\" tab at the bottom of the Map interface. A popup will appear that will prompt you to click on either \"Export Interventions\" or \"Add Intervention\".\" Click on the latter. This will prompt a new window to appear called \"Intervention Input Form\"\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-896 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ANALYST_Intervention_Input_Form_1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1366\" height=\"1203\" />\r\n\r\nFrom here, Analyst users may select the type of intervention made through a dropdown list available in the \"Intervention Detail\" category.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-897 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ANALYST_Intervention_Options.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"590\" />\r\n\r\nClicking on \"Save Intervention\" will then add the intervention on the DRIVER database.[:]', '[:en]Adding Interventions[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '891-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-04 01:09:36', '2017-10-04 01:09:36', '', 891, 'http://roadsafety.ph/891-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(900, 1, '2017-10-04 01:21:35', '2017-10-04 01:21:35', '[:en]Analyst users on DRIVER have access to additional information not available to Public Viewer users. These are: Vehicle Type, People [Involved in the Incident], and Photos.\r\n<h3>Accessing Analyst-Exclusive Data</h3>\r\nNew tabs will appear within the individual incident details. Users may toggle between the \"Vehicle Type\", \"People\", and \"Photo\" tab to view further information on the incident.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-903 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ANALYST_People_Tab.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"764\" height=\"324\" />\r\n<h3>Analyst Filters</h3>\r\nAn additional filter called \"Vehicle Type\" is accessible to Analyst users through the white header bar above both the Map and the Record List.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-901 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ANALYST_Vehicle_True.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1365\" height=\"636\" />[:]', '[:en]Analyst-Exclusive Data[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'analyst-exclusive-data', '', '', '2017-10-04 01:22:22', '2017-10-04 01:22:22', '', 0, 'http://roadsafety.ph/?p=900', 0, 'post', '', 0),
