(1062, 1, '2017-10-06 12:11:44', '2017-10-06 12:11:44', '[:en]To add new users, simply click on the \"Add New User\" button under the User Management page, which you can access by clicking \"Manage Users\" on the top right corner of the Ashlar Editor.\r\n\r\nUpon clicking the \"Add New User\" button, the Ashlar Editor will redirect you to a new page labelled \"Create User Account\".\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1063 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Create-User-Account.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"912\" height=\"353\" />\r\n\r\nFrom here, you may create a user by filling the necessary details shown, as well as provide the user with a password.\r\n\r\nClick on the \"CreateUser\" button below to create the user account.[:]', '[:en]Adding New Users[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'adding-new-users', '', '', '2017-10-06 14:39:36', '2017-10-06 14:39:36', '', 0, 'http://roadsafety.ph/?p=1062', 0, 'post', '', 0),
