(1065, 1, '2017-10-06 12:43:55', '2017-10-06 12:43:55', '[:en]Record Types on the DRIVER website may be added via the Ashlar Schema Editor. As of the moment, there are two Record Types on the DRIVER website: Incidents and Interventions.\r\n<h3><img class=\"wp-image-1066 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Record-Types.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"199\" height=\"425\" />\r\nView All Record Types</h3>\r\nThese two Record Types (and succeeding record types) may be viewed in the Ashlar Editor on the sidebar seen on the left. Clicking on the \"View all record types\" button takes the user to the available record types, where they can add, edit, or delete details of their selected Record Type.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1068 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/All-Record-Types.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"920\" height=\"193\" />\r\n\r\nClicking on the \"Preview\" button on the far right of the Record Type will take the user to a preview of the Record Type\'s Input Form on the DRIVER website. In the preview, users may click the \"Expand\" button to view more details of the Record Type\'s input form.\r\n<h3>Editing Record Types</h3>\r\nClicking on the \"Edit\" button on the right side of each Record Type entry will let admin users edit its details, which will reflect on the DRIVER website.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1102 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Edit-Record-Type.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"946\" height=\"381\" />\r\n<h3>Deleting Record Types</h3>\r\nTo delete Record Types, simply click on the \"Trash\" button located on the rightmost side of each Record Type entry.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1103 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Incident-trash.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"886\" height=\"63\" />[:]', '[:en]Record Types[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'record-types', '', '', '2017-10-06 15:58:44', '2017-10-06 15:58:44', '', 0, 'http://roadsafety.ph/?p=1065', 0, 'post', '', 0),
