(1086, 1, '2017-10-06 14:19:19', '2017-10-06 14:19:19', '[:en]The DRIVER website displays two widgets that calculate Economic Loss &amp; Societal Harm. These widgets\' results also adjust according to what filters are set by the user.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1087 size-full\" src=\"http://roadsafety.ph/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Cost-Aggregation-Settings.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"945\" height=\"563\" />\r\nTo set costs for economic loss and societal harm, expand the Incidents navigation tab and click on “Cost aggregation settings”.\r\n\r\nThe interface provides formatting options for currency, the type of content, and field to associate with\r\ncosts. Only option-type fields are available for associating costs.[:]', '[:en]Economic Loss & Societal Harm[:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'economic-loss-societal-harm', '', '', '2017-10-06 14:19:19', '2017-10-06 14:19:19', '', 0, 'http://roadsafety.ph/?p=1086', 0, 'post', '', 0),
